{"calories":"770","carbs":null,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"Thanks to a test kitchen-devised shortcut, we’ve mastered fresh, homemade  ricotta—in under 20 minutes! In this vibrant summery dish, al dente fusilli pasta is coated with a sultry tomato-pesto sauce, which gets layers of flavor from sun-dried and plum tomatoes, pecorino cheese, and a hit of Aleppo pepper. Finished with fluffy homemade ricotta and and fragrant basil, this meal is one for the ages. ","difficulty":"medium","external_id":"69376650c9","fat":null,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/12930/Fusilli_Pasta_with_Pesto_Rosso_and_Fresh_Ricotta-HERO.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/12930/hero_Fusilli_Pasta_with_Pesto_Rosso_and_Fresh_Ricotta-HERO.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/12930/menu_small_Fusilli_Pasta_with_Pesto_Rosso_and_Fresh_Ricotta-HERO.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/12930/small_square_Fusilli_Pasta_with_Pesto_Rosso_and_Fresh_Ricotta-HERO.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/12930/medium_square_Fusilli_Pasta_with_Pesto_Rosso_and_Fresh_Ricotta-HERO.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/12930/recipe_profile_page_Fusilli_Pasta_with_Pesto_Rosso_and_Fresh_Ricotta-HERO.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/12932/Fusilli_Pasta_with_Pesto_Rosso_and_Fresh_Ricotta-THUMB.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/12932/menu_small_Fusilli_Pasta_with_Pesto_Rosso_and_Fresh_Ricotta-THUMB.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/12931/Fusilli_Pasta_with_Pesto_Rosso_and_Fresh_Ricotta-MOBILE.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}},{"image":{"url":"/assets/blank_profile-62376be1ebee267193d25c20f8cd8bc5a6c47743a4a323d32a54ecdf231b7b80.png","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}}],"name":"Fusilli with Homemade Ricotta and Pesto Rosso","novice_time":"","portion_count":2,"prep_time":"35-45","pro_time":"","product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":null,"public_slug":"fusilli-with-homemade-ricotta-and-pesto-rosso","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/7437/recipe_card20160801-3-103gtay.pdf","recipe_id":1537,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Fusilli with Ricotta","subtitle":"and Pesto Rosso","title":"Fusilli with Homemade Ricotta","legal_copy_short":null,"available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"Be sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking.\n\nNo microwave? No worries! Bring milk and .5 teaspoon salt to a simmer over medium-high heat. Once simmering and small bubbles are forming on the surface, add vinegar and continue to cook, stirring occasionally, until mixture curdles. Remove from heat, let stand 15 minutes and drain over cheesecloth as below. \n\nWhile it cooks, pasta will release starches into the boiling water. Adding some reserved pasta water to the sauce will help it bind with the noodles. ","equipment":["10\" large pot ","microwave","12\" large pan"],"id":1537,"ingredients":["plum tomatoes","garlic","sun-dried tomatoes","basil","milk","white vinegar","fusilli pasta","Aleppo pepper","white wine","pesto","grated pecorino cheese","cheesecloth"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"plum tomatoes","quantity":"3.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/92/medium_square_veg-plum-tomatoes.jpg"},{"name":"garlic","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"clove","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2/medium_square_GARLIC_PEELED_copy.jpg"},{"name":"sun-dried tomatoes","quantity":"5.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/169/medium_square_sundried-tomatoes.jpg"},{"name":"basil","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1276/medium_square_medium_square_basil-test.jpg"},{"name":"milk","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"pint","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1413/medium_square_medium_square_coconut-milk.jpg"},{"name":"white vinegar","quantity":"0.25","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/91/medium_square_white-vinegar-test.jpg"},{"name":"fusilli pasta","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1445/medium_square_sfoglini_fusili.jpg"},{"name":"Aleppo pepper","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"teaspoon","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/80/medium_square_spice-cayenne-pepper-test_copy.jpg"},{"name":"white wine","quantity":"0.25","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/256/medium_square_WHITE_WINE_copy.jpg"},{"name":"pesto","quantity":"0.33","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1075/medium_square_PESTO_-4396_copy.jpg"},{"name":"grated pecorino cheese","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/539/medium_square_parmesan-cheese-2.jpg"},{"name":"cheesecloth","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":12,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/620/medium_square_cheesecloth.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":[],"pantry_items_full":[],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare Ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/11777/recipe_card_size_1._Prepare_Ingredients.jpg","description":"Bring a large pot of water to a boil over high heat. Rinse all produce. Roughly chop \u003cb\u003eplum tomatoes\u003c/b\u003e. Mince \u003cb\u003egarlic\u003c/b\u003e. Finely chop \u003cb\u003esun-dried tomatoes\u003c/b\u003e. Finely chop \u003cb\u003ebasil\u003c/b\u003e leaves, discarding stems. Fold \u003cb\u003echeesecloth\u003c/b\u003e in half. Line a fine strainer or colander with cheesecloth. Place over a large bowl. "},{"title":"Make Ricotta","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/11778/recipe_card_size_2._Make_Ricotta.jpg","description":"In a medium microwave-safe bowl, whisk together \u003cb\u003emilk\u003c/b\u003e, \u003cb\u003evinegar\u003c/b\u003e, and \u003cb\u003e.5 teaspoon salt\u003c/b\u003e. Microwave until cheese curds form and separate from liquid, 7-9 minutes (see Recipe Tip). Carefully pour \u003cb\u003ericotta mixture\u003c/b\u003e through cheesecloth into bowl, allowing liquids to fall through and solids to remain. Allow to sit and drain for 5 minutes. Wring out cheesecloth, removing excess moisture from cheese, then place \u003cb\u003ericotta\u003c/b\u003e in a small bowl and fluff with a fork. "},{"title":"Cook Fusilli","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/11779/recipe_card_size_3._Cook_Fusilli.jpg","description":"While ricotta drains, generously season boiling water with \u003cb\u003esalt\u003c/b\u003e, then add \u003cb\u003efusilli\u003c/b\u003e.  Cook until noodles are al dente, 5-8 minutes. Reserve \u003cb\u003e1 cup pasta cooking water\u003c/b\u003e, then drain. "},{"title":"Make Pesto Rosso ","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/11780/recipe_card_size_4._Make_Pesto_Rosso.jpg","description":"While pasta cooks, heat \u003cb\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/b\u003e in a large pan over medium heat. When oil is shimmering, add \u003cb\u003eplum tomatoes\u003c/b\u003e, \u003cb\u003egarlic\u003c/b\u003e, \u003cb\u003esun-dried tomatoes\u003c/b\u003e, and as much \u003cb\u003eAleppo pepper\u003c/b\u003e as desired (it's spicy!) Cook, breaking up \u003cb\u003etomatoes\u003c/b\u003e with a spoon, until softened, about 5 minutes.  Add \u003cb\u003ewhite wine\u003c/b\u003e to pan and cook until reduced by half, 4 minutes more. Stir in \u003cb\u003epesto\u003c/b\u003e to combine. "},{"title":"Season Pasta","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/11781/recipe_card_size_5._Season_Pasta_2.jpg","description":" Add \u003cb\u003efusilli\u003c/b\u003e to pan with sauce over medium heat and cook, stirring, until noodles are warmed through, 1-2 minutes. Add \u003cb\u003ereserved pasta cooking water\u003c/b\u003e, 1 tablespoon at a time, until sauce is thick and clings to noodles (see Recipe Tip). Add \u003cb\u003epecorino\u003c/b\u003e and toss to combine. Taste and add more \u003cb\u003esalt\u003c/b\u003e and \u003cb\u003eblack pepper\u003c/b\u003e as needed."},{"title":"Plate Pasta","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/11782/recipe_card_size_6._Plate_Pasta.jpg","description":"Taste \u003cb\u003ericotta\u003c/b\u003e and add \u003cb\u003esalt\u003c/b\u003e if desired. Divide \u003cb\u003epasta\u003c/b\u003e between 2 bowls and dollop on \u003cb\u003efresh ricotta\u003c/b\u003e. Garnish with \u003cb\u003ebasil\u003c/b\u003e and enjoy your gorgeous, homemade meal. "}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Stovetop only","slug":"stovetop-only","hex_color":""}],"allergens":[],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Pasta","slug":"pasta","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Stovetop only","slug":"stovetop-only","hex_color":""}],"feature":[]}}